{"word":"H2268 - חֶבֶר - Cheber - kheh'-ber - Heber","slug":"H2268","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֶבֶר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Cheber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kheh'-ber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Heber"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>חבר</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>cheber</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>kheh'-ber</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Heber = \"comrade\" <ol><li>the Kenite, husband of Jael, who slew Sisera by driving a nail into his temple</li><li>grandson of Asher from whom came the Heberites</li><li>father of Socho, a Judahite</li><li>a Benjamite</li><li>another Benjamite</li><li>a Gadite</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H2267\">H2267</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2249\">H2249</a>, <a href=\"#/H2250\">H2250</a>, <a href=\"#/H2266\">H2266</a>, <a href=\"#/H2267\">H2267</a>, <a href=\"#/H2270\">H2270</a>, <a href=\"#/H2271\">H2271</a>, <a href=\"#/H2272\">H2272</a>, <a href=\"#/H2274\">H2274</a>, <a href=\"#/H2275\">H2275</a>, <a href=\"#/H2276\">H2276</a>, <a href=\"#/H2277\">H2277</a>, <a href=\"#/H2278\">H2278</a>, <a href=\"#/H2279\">H2279</a>, <a href=\"#/H4225\">H4225</a>, <a href=\"#/H4226\">H4226</a>"}]}